            . This is the pot I fetched from Mr. Ratcliff's house. Guilty.</p>
               <p>+ John Smith, was a second time indicted for stealing a silk gown, value 55 s. a cotton gown, value 10 s. a cloak, value 4 s. two yards of black silk, val. 6 s. a calimanco quilted petcoat, value 15 s. a white linen petticoat, value 14 d. a pair of sheets, value 12 s. five aprons,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="174502270006"></xptr> value 10 s. three aprons, value 2 s. eight handkerchiefs, value 12 s. two pair of shift sleeves, 8 d. one pair of shirt sleeves, value 2 s. a pair of stays, value 5 s. a shirt, value 4 s. four caps, value 4 s. two tea spoons, value 2 s. 6 d. and a blanket, value 2 s. &amp;c. the goods of 
